<xml xmlns="https://developers.google.com/blockly/xml"><variables><variable id="[:Zrv3%?Ecf:@[h4.TcX">milliliters_to_draw</variable><variable id="1P9x-P!$;r%6(h$fsDTE">pump_speed</variable><variable id=";$gsLh5GPpWx:lpr0W-M">total_cup_capcity_ml</variable><variable id="]sx2yu?1(3G6fk0U:wMR">time_to_fill</variable><variable id="pd]|v}PxU`C[;ps=o_1r">time_to_fill_1ml</variable><variable id="(LLPm{si5@U8vM#mgEK]">pump_running</variable><variable id="+7-19e:7T=Nvif|.rVg(">test_to_get_time_to_fill_cup</variable><variable id="v[Lmn_;a!feWwkOgS!1i">test_duration_secs</variable><variable id="DboogO5fXAi9ydhFlHKi">time_to_fill_cup</variable></variables><comment id="5*G~D7l.2QAr~5}F{fi7" x="0" y="0" w="480" h="120">
if pump_speed is greater then 255 or less then -255 it defaults to the closest valid integer
if you change the pump_speed, record the time it takes to fill the cup up again
</comment><comment id="u|pW:!Df.R,kS8+I/=ad" x="0" y="0" w="480" h="360">
error codes:
ml: the milliliters_to_draw is greater than the cup's total capacity
lib: the SuperBitV2 library was either not found/installed or SuperBitV2.enMotors.M1 was not found

normal codes:
O: on, nothing running
T: test to get time running
P: pump started/is running
FINI: pump finished running
</comment><comment id="(l?nLCB[|{tThWo19c*0" x="0" y="0" w="480" h="360">
basic.forever(function () {
if (!pump_running &amp;&amp; input.buttonIsPressed(Button.A)) {
if (!test_to_get_time_to_fill_cup) {
showString("P")
pump_running = true
DrawMilliliters(milliliters_to_draw)
pump_running = false
} else {
showString("T")
pump_running = true
RunPump(test_duration_secs * 1000)
pump_running = false
}


}
})
</comment><block type="pxt-on-start" id="#DHvjog^9]I!Km(lLt2[" x="9" y="64"><statement name="HANDLER"><block type="variables_set" id="d.pDElbcE;X%XSFl^Uzc"><field name="VAR" id="+7-19e:7T=Nvif|.rVg(">test_to_get_time_to_fill_cup</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="5V~%KM?Dn$iWt8S2}9Pf"><field name="NUM">0</field></shadow><block type="logic_boolean" id="cHRNIG^OMh=@hjTUB^])"><field name="BOOL">TRUE</field></block></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="Go%=4*=$L)3V1|xMN_xS"><field name="VAR" id="v[Lmn_;a!feWwkOgS!1i">test_duration_secs</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="8x:mbq2]6pN;6^Kq2GZg"><field name="NUM">10</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id=":.FFMOkWv:yf,BB*llWX"><field name="VAR" id="1P9x-P!$;r%6(h$fsDTE">pump_speed</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="6NS^L6QSnO^r^S[}LO{@"><field name="NUM">255</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="A}c5|iE:^8cZNDuin]^h"><field name="VAR" id="[:Zrv3%?Ecf:@[h4.TcX">milliliters_to_draw</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="JyY;#O+*Q`L!@LgIzY9v"><field name="NUM">250</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="`*_^t|h{R%WTf$JyE~$H"><field name="VAR" id=";$gsLh5GPpWx:lpr0W-M">total_cup_capcity_ml</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="}19=,?sK`$GZ/JuSwo4J"><field name="NUM">798</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="sC*Yjh6.n5pQhx:3gn7="><field name="VAR" id="DboogO5fXAi9ydhFlHKi">time_to_fill_cup</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="Y%dNh@d@}Hez$}9!PGy0"><field name="NUM">10</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="+6iol(Gw#MTo@E|_GAfU"><field name="VAR" id="pd]|v}PxU`C[;ps=o_1r">time_to_fill_1ml</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="+26(r~qUR1^yGlQG1G/("><field name="NUM">0</field></shadow><block type="math_arithmetic" id=";Fy@E=~r.BlylZm4+Ku)"><field name="OP">DIVIDE</